    <title>P1869 дә’дёҚдҫөзҠҜ йўҳи§Ј</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/09/15/solution-P1869/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/09/15/solution-P1869/</id>
    <published>2022-09-14T16:31:54.367Z</published>
    <updated>2022-11-08T00:49:54.412Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>гҖҖгҖҖгҖҖгҖҖ</p><span id="more"></span><p><a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P1896">йўҳзӣ®дј йҖҒй—Ё</a></p><h2 id="жҖқи·Ҝ"><a href="#жҖқи·Ҝ" class="headerlink" title="жҖқи·Ҝ"></a>жҖқи·Ҝ</h2><p>еҜ№дәҺжҜҸдёҖиЎҢпјҢжҲ‘д»¬еҸҜд»Ҙе°Ҷе®ғи®ҫзҪ®дёәдёҖдёӘзҠ¶жҖҒгҖӮ</p><p>жҜ”еҰӮиҝҷдёҖиЎҢпјҡ</p><p><img src="https://tuchuangs.com/imgs/2022/09/15/91e1134fa0497c81.jpg" alt=""></p><p>пјҲзәўзҡ„жҳҜеӣҪзҺӢпјҢзҷҪзҡ„дёәз©әпјү</p><p>еҒҮи®ҫз©әзҡ„дёә $0$пјҢеӣҪзҺӢдёә $1$пјҢйӮЈд№ҲиҝҷдёҖиЎҢзҡ„зҠ¶жҖҒе°ұеҸҜд»ҘиЎЁзӨәдёә $0100101$гҖӮ</p><p>жҠҠ $0100101$ зңӢдҪңжҳҜдёҖдёӘдәҢиҝӣеҲ¶ж•°пјҢйӮЈд№Ҳе®ғзҡ„еҚҒиҝӣеҲ¶дёә $37$гҖӮ</p><p>жҲ‘д»¬дёҚйңҖиҰҒеӯҳеӮЁ $0100101$пјҢеҸӘеӯҳеӮЁ $37$ еҚіеҸҜгҖӮиҝҷе°ұжҳҜжң¬йўҳзҠ¶жҖҒеҺӢзј©зҡ„жҖқи·ҜгҖӮ</p><p>еӣ жӯӨжҲ‘д»¬з§°иҝҷдёҖиЎҢзҡ„зҠ¶жҖҒдёә $37$гҖӮ</p><hr><p>ж №жҚ®йўҳж„ҸеҸҜеҫ—пјҢеҪ“дёҖиЎҢеҶ…жІЎжңүзӣёйӮ»зҡ„еӣҪзҺӢж—¶пјҢиҝҷдёҖиЎҢе°ұжҲҗз«ӢгҖӮ</p><p>йӮЈд№ҲпјҢжҲ‘д»¬еҰӮдҪ•еҲӨж–ӯдёҖдёӘзҠ¶жҖҒжҳҜеҗҰжҲҗз«Ӣе‘ўпјҹ</p><p>дёҚйҡҫжғіеҲ°пјҢеҸҜд»Ҙ $\mathcal{O}(n)$ жһҡдёҫпјҢдҪҶиҝҷж ·йҖҹеәҰеӨӘж…ўгҖӮ</p><p>йӮЈд№ҲпјҢжҲ‘д»¬е°ұиҰҒз”ЁеҲ°дёӢйқўеҮ дёӘдҪҚиҝҗз®—гҖӮ</p><ol><li><code>a &amp; b</code>пјҡжҢүдҪҚдёҺгҖӮеҪ“дәҢиҝӣеҲ¶ж•° $a$ дёҺ $b$ дёҚеӯҳеңЁеҗҢдёҖдҪҚйғҪдёә $1$пјҢз»“жһңе°ұдёә $0$гҖӮ</li><li><code>a &lt;&lt; 1</code>пјҡе·Ұз§»гҖӮе°ҶдәҢиҝӣеҲ¶ж•° $a$ зҡ„жүҖжңүдҪҚзҪ®дёҠзҡ„ж•°еӯ—еҗ‘е·Ұз§»еҠЁдёҖдҪҚгҖӮ</li><li><code>a &gt;&gt; 1</code>пјҡеҸіз§»гҖӮе°ҶдәҢиҝӣеҲ¶ж•° $a$ зҡ„жүҖжңүдҪҚзҪ®дёҠзҡ„ж•°еӯ—еҗ‘еҸіз§»еҠЁдёҖдҪҚгҖӮ</li></ol><p>еҒҮи®ҫжӯӨиЎҢзҡ„зҠ¶жҖҒдёә $a$гҖӮпјҲ$a$ жҳҜдёҖдёӘдәҢиҝӣеҲ¶ж•° пјү</p><p>жҲ‘д»¬е…Ҳе°Ҷ $a$ е·Ұз§»дёҖдҪҚпјҢеҶҚдёҺеҺҹе§Ӣзҡ„ $a$ еҜ№йҪҗ</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">еҺҹе§Ӣзҡ„aпјҡ          a[1] a[2] a[3]  </span><br><span class="line">е·Ұз§»дёҖдҪҚеҗҺзҡ„aпјҡa[1] a[2] a[3] a[4]...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>иҝҷж ·пјҢжҲ‘д»¬е°ұжҠҠ $a_i$ е’Ң $a_{i+1}$ еҜ№йҪҗдәҶгҖӮ</p><p>е°ҶиҝҷдёӨдёӘж•°иҝӣиЎҢжҢүдҪҚдёҺиҝҗз®—гҖӮ</p><p>еҰӮжһңиҝ”еӣһеҖјдёә $0$пјҢиҜҙжҳҺдёҚеӯҳеңЁ $a_i$ е’Ң $a_{i+1}$ йғҪдёә $1$ зҡ„жғ…еҶөгҖӮ</p><p>жүҖд»ҘеҸҜеҫ—пјҢеҪ“ <code>(a&amp;(a&lt;&lt;1))==0)</code>ж—¶пјҢзҠ¶жҖҒ $a$ жҲҗз«ӢгҖӮ</p><hr><p>еҶҚжҖқиҖғпјҢд»Җд№ҲжқЎд»¶дёӢпјҢдёҠйқўдёҖиЎҢзҡ„зҠ¶жҖҒдёә $s1$пјҢдёӢйқўдёҖиЎҢзҡ„зҠ¶жҖҒдёә $s2$пјҢдё”дёҠдёӢдёҚеҶІзӘҒгҖӮ</p><p>еҒҮи®ҫдёҠйқўдёҖиЎҢзҡ„з¬¬ $i$ дҪҚдёә $1$ пјҢйӮЈд№ҲдёӢйқўдёҖиЎҢзҡ„з¬¬ $i-1$гҖҒ$i$гҖҒ$i+1$ дҪҚйғҪдёҚиғҪжҳҜ $1$гҖӮ</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>е…Ҳе°Ҷ $s1$ дёҺ $s2$ еҜ№йҪҗ</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">s1пјҡs1[1] s1[2] s1[3] s1[4]...</span><br><span class="line">s2пјҡs2[1] s2[2] s2[3] s2[4]...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>жӯӨж—¶ $s1_i$ дёҺ $s2_i$ еҜ№йҪҗгҖӮ</p><p>е°Ҷ $s1$ дёҺ $s2$ иҝӣиЎҢжҢүдҪҚдёҺиҝҗз®—гҖӮеҰӮжһңиҝ”еӣһеҖјдёә $0$пјҢе°ұиҜҙжҳҺдёҚеӯҳеңЁ $s1_i$ дёҺ $s2_i$ йғҪдёә $1$гҖӮ </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>еҶҚе°Ҷ $s1$ дёҺ е·Ұз§»дёҖдҪҚзҡ„$s2$ еҜ№йҪҗгҖӮ</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">s1пјҡ      s1[1] s1[2] s1[3]...</span><br><span class="line">s2пјҡs2[1] s2[2] s2[3] s2[4]...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>жӯӨж—¶ $s1_i$ дёҺ $s2_{i+1}$ еҜ№йҪҗ</p><p>е°Ҷ $s1$ дёҺ е·Ұз§»дёҖдҪҚзҡ„$s2$ иҝӣиЎҢжҢүдҪҚдёҺиҝҗз®—гҖӮеҰӮжһңиҝ”еӣһеҖјдёә $0$пјҢе°ұиҜҙжҳҺдёҚеӯҳеңЁ $s1_i$ дёҺ $s2_{i+1}$ йғҪдёә $1$гҖӮ</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>жңҖеҗҺе°Ҷ $s1$ дёҺ еҸіз§»дёҖдҪҚзҡ„$s2$ еҜ№йҪҗгҖӮ</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">s1пјҡs1[1] s1[2] s1[3] s1[4]...</span><br><span class="line">s2пјҡ      s2[1] s2[2] s2[3]...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>жӯӨж—¶ $s1_i$ дёҺ $s2_{i-1}$ еҜ№йҪҗ</p><p>е°Ҷ $s1$ дёҺ еҸіз§»дёҖдҪҚзҡ„$s2$ иҝӣиЎҢжҢүдҪҚдёҺиҝҗз®—гҖӮеҰӮжһңиҝ”еӣһеҖјдёә $0$пјҢе°ұиҜҙжҳҺдёҚеӯҳеңЁ $s1_i$ дёҺ $s2_{i-1}$ йғҪдёә $1$гҖӮ</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>еҰӮжһңдёҠйқўзҡ„дёүдёӘжқЎд»¶йғҪж»Ўи¶іпјҢе°ұиҜҙжҳҺпјҡеҪ“ $s1_i=1$ ж—¶пјҢ$s2_{i-1}$гҖҒ$s2_{i}$гҖҒ$s2_{i+1}$ йғҪдёҚдёә $1$ гҖӮ</p><p>жүҖд»ҘеҸҜеҫ—пјҢеҪ“ <code>(s1&amp;s2==0)&amp;&amp;(s1&amp;(s2&lt;&lt;1))==0)&amp;&amp;((s1&amp;(s2&gt;&gt;1))==0)</code>ж—¶пјҢ$s1$ дёҺ $s2$ дёҚеҶІзӘҒгҖӮ</p><hr><p>жҺҘдёӢжқҘжҺЁиҪ¬з§»ж–№зЁӢејҸ.</p><p>еҒҮи®ҫ $dp[i][j][k]$ иЎЁзӨәз¬¬ $i$ иЎҢпјҢдҪҝз”ЁдәҶ $j$ дёӘеӣҪзҺӢпјҢжӯӨиЎҢзҡ„зҠ¶жҖҒдёә $k$ зҡ„ж–№жЎҲж•°гҖӮ</p><p>йӮЈд№ҲпјҢиӢҘзҺ°еңЁдёәз¬¬ $i$ иЎҢпјҢдҪҝз”ЁдәҶ $l$ дёӘеӣҪзҺӢпјҢеҪ“еүҚиЎҢзҠ¶жҖҒдёә $s2$пјҢдёҠдёҖиЎҢзҠ¶жҖҒдёә $s1$пјҢиҪ¬з§»ж–№зЁӢе°ұжҳҜ <code>dp[i][l][s2]+=dp[i-1][l-cnt_king[s2]][s1];</code></p><p>жіЁпјҡ<code>cnt_king[s2]</code> дёәзҠ¶жҖҒдёә $s2$ зҡ„еӣҪзҺӢдёӘж•°гҖӮ</p><hr><h2 id="е®Ңж•ҙд»Јз Ғ"><a href="#е®Ңж•ҙд»Јз Ғ" class="headerlink" title="е®Ңж•ҙд»Јз Ғ"></a>е®Ңж•ҙд»Јз Ғ</h2><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span><span class="string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> n,k;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> cnt_king[<span class="number">3000</span>];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> dp[<span class="number">10</span>][<span class="number">100</span>][<span class="number">3000</span>];</span><br><span class="line">vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; p;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ios::<span class="built_in">sync_with_stdio</span>(<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    cin.<span class="built_in">tie</span>(<span class="number">0</span>);cout.<span class="built_in">tie</span>(<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    cin&gt;&gt;n&gt;&gt;k;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;(<span class="number">1</span>&lt;&lt;n);i++)<span class="comment">//жһҡдёҫжҜҸдёҖдёӘзҠ¶жҖҒпјҢзҠ¶жҖҒж•°йҮҸдёә 2^n дёӘ</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> x=i,res=<span class="number">0</span>;<span class="comment">//res:зҠ¶жҖҒдёәiж—¶пјҢеӣҪзҺӢзҡ„дёӘж•°</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span>(x)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            x-=(x&amp;-x);<span class="comment">//еҮҸеҺ»жңҖдҪҺдҪҚзҡ„1</span></span><br><span class="line">            res++;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        cnt_king[i]=res;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(((i&amp;(i&lt;&lt;<span class="number">1</span>))==<span class="number">0</span>)) p.<span class="built_in">push_back</span>(i);<span class="comment">//еҲӨж–ӯiжҳҜеҗҰеҗҲжі•гҖӮеҰӮжһңеҗҲжі•пјҢе°ұеҠ е…ҘpйҮҢ</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    dp[<span class="number">0</span>][<span class="number">0</span>][<span class="number">0</span>]=<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">1</span>;i&lt;=n;i++)<span class="comment">//еҪ“еүҚжҳҜз¬¬iиЎҢ</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> j=<span class="number">0</span>;j&lt;p.<span class="built_in">size</span>();j++)<span class="comment">//жһҡдёҫеҪ“еүҚиЎҢзҡ„зҠ¶жҖҒ</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">int</span> s2=p[j];</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> m=<span class="number">0</span>;m&lt;p.<span class="built_in">size</span>();m++)<span class="comment">//жһҡдёҫдёҠйқўиЎҢзҡ„зҠ¶жҖҒ</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="type">int</span> s1=p[m];</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span>(!(((s1&amp;s2)==<span class="number">0</span>)&amp;&amp;((s1&amp;(s2&lt;&lt;<span class="number">1</span>))==<span class="number">0</span>)&amp;&amp;((s1&amp;(s2&gt;&gt;<span class="number">1</span>))==<span class="number">0</span>))) </span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">continue</span>;<span class="comment">//еҰӮжһңдёҚеҗҲжі•пјҢе°ұзӣҙжҺҘи·іиҝҮ</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">                 <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> l=cnt_king[s2];l&lt;=k;l++) <span class="comment">//йҒҚеҺҶеӣҪзҺӢдёӘж•°</span></span><br><span class="line">                    dp[i][l][s2]+=dp[i<span class="number">-1</span>][l-cnt_king[s2]][s1];<span class="comment">//иҪ¬з§»ж–№зЁӢ</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> ans=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;p.<span class="built_in">size</span>();i++) </span><br><span class="line">        ans+=dp[n][k][p[i]];<span class="comment">//е°ҶжңҖеҗҺдёҖиЎҢпјҢеӣҪзҺӢдёӘж•°дёәkпјҢжүҖжңүзҠ¶жҖҒзҡ„ж–№жЎҲж•°зӣёеҠ </span></span><br><span class="line">    cout&lt;&lt;ans;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>пјӣ</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr>]]></content>
    
    
